<header class="posts">
	<div class="posts-header">
	  <h1 class="brand-heading">Welcome!</h1>
    <p>HAGGLER's here to connect people looking for great deals. Wanna trade your sofa for a microwave? Maybe offer your git skills in exchange for a 1990s Honda Civic? Whatever it is, you're sure to find a trade here.</p>
    <p>Check out the latest goods and skills listed below, or if you've got something to offer, <a href="/users/new">register for an account!</a></p>
	</div>
  <div class="container-posts">
		<h1 class="brand-heading">Recent Posts</h1>
    <p>
			<% if @posts.any? %>
        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
  			<div>
  				<h3 class="posts-heading"><a href="/posts/<%= post.id %>"><%= post.title %></a></h3>
          <p class="posts-user-info">Posted in <span><a href="/posts/category/<%= post.category %>" class="posts-category"><%= post.category %></a></span>
            <input type="hidden" name="category" value="<%= post.category %>" /> by: <%= post.user.email %> on <%= post.created_at %></p>
  			</div>
      <% end %>
		<% end %>
  </div>
</header>
